Oppose - I think such incidents are very rare. A solution looking for a problem. Kudpung à¸à¸¸à¸”à¸œà¸¶à¹‰à¸‡ (talk) 13:31, 20 January 2016 (UTC)
Oppose - Sorry to pile on but I occasionally use the edit function on prev revisions to remove vandalism .... No need to remove the feature IMHO. â€“Davey2010Talk 13:55, 20 January 2016 (UTC)
